My First C++ Programm
=====================
Following an old tradition we will start with the following example:

:import: test/hello.cc [downloadable,stripped,file=test/hello_stripped.cc]

And here unstripped

:import: test/hello.cc [downloadable]

Compile and Run
===============
From the terminal we compile and execute the example:

--- SHELL ----------------------------------------------------------------------
cd test
g++ -Wall -o hello hello.cc
./hello
